caller_intent: Judy is following up on a pending insurance policy, inquiring about the status of mailed paperwork and seeking assistance with processing a money order refund for a canceled policy.
resolution_steps: Brandi confirms the policy is still pending and explains the document is being mailed but not yet received.
Brandi suggests Judy can visit the Winston office to sign the old policy paperwork.
Brandi offers to help Judy request a refund for the money order but notes office computers have restricted access to certain websites.
Brandi agrees to call Judy once the new policy document arrives.
knowledge_required: Office location accessibility for document signing
Internal system security restrictions for website access
summary: Judy discusses a pending insurance policy and needs help with paperwork and a money order refund. Brandi explains the document mailing timeline, suggests visiting the Winston office, and discusses refund process limitations due to office security systems. A follow-up call is scheduled once the new policy document arrives.
